keyFacts: The document is a fragment of administrative logs from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York, dated August 9-10, 2019.
It lists specific computer workstations (279, 283, 236) used to complete lieutenant rounds, indicating routine prison operations.
The document is marked 'CONFIDENTIAL' and is part of the Epstein case files (SDNY_00010790, EFTA00139514).
The timeframe (August 9-10, 2019) is significant as it falls just days before Jeffrey Epstein's death in custody at the MCC on August 10, 2019.
